,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T16:07:26.000Z","msg":"又係D傻西毒撚，有女同佢傾兩句就沉撚曬船<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nText下佢就認定呢個係一生中最愛，非卿不娶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住開始傷春悲秋，覺得自己陷入苦戀，凄美浪漫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個女仔同男仔傾兩句，就覺得有人比帽佢戴，嬲到震曬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好快就會忍唔住戇撚尻尻，死就死唔做實後悔，唔照下鏡先，自殺式表白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n毒撚表白嚇死條女，派好人卡，再Block尻佢，毒撚就開始惱羞成怒發爛渣，怪條女做乜比錯覺佢，賤格收佢做兵，冇興趣做乜要同我傾計同我text，之後再上高登屌條女係雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n憤怒過後，自我陶醉自覺經歷失戀，再次傷春悲秋，認定自己受到情傷，曾經滄海難為水，除卻巫山不是雲，再自命看透世事，「自我選擇」拒絕動情，一個人自在更開心，全部女人都係雞！溝女既係狗公MK！拍拖既直刻死！撞車死！生Cancer！換唔到心死！抵撚死！哈哈哈！全部係雞！全部都蝦尻毒撚！全部仆街死！哈哈..哈！！<br />\n<br />\n毒撚，Are you ready?!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5efde6d8e75fd8be565a83bed390be8134ef34b3","tid":480943,"uid":143454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T16:11:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cdab1ed216012eda4cc63b31b8344dd6eb3eb4e6","tid":480943,"uid":30049,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T16:40:36.000Z","msg":"他們想要強奸我"},{"pid":"3693107de9232196da10342e5ec734a641de922e","tid":480943,"uid":7306,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T08:44:41.000Z","msg":"想幫佢埋單<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7a36a1ac80fb62d9d6af49515a80611a0c2f890","tid":48